<title>Tulasi Technologies</title>
<body style="font:Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:11px">
<div id="ordertocash_trans_addpackslip">
<p><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Add New Pack Slip </b></p>
<ol><b>To Add new Pack Slip</b>
<li>You have to select the values of "Party", "Sales Order #", "Date", "Transporter" and "Type of Bag"(In the dropdown available below the "No.Of" column.)</li>
<li>You have to select the "Mode of Transportation".<br/>
<ol>If selected value of Mode of Transportation is "By Air" you have to enter value for "AW #".</ol>
<ol>If selected value of Mode of Transportation is "By Road" you have to enter the value for "LR #" and "Driver".</ol>
<ol>If selected value of Mode of Transportation is "By Train" you have to enter the value for "RR #".</ol></li>
<li>You have to enter the values for "No.Of"(no. of Bags), "Time of Dispatch" and "Freight".</li>
<li>You can also enter "Lot#" and "Serial#" if the <b>Select</b> value of Ordered Item Code given in the <b>Inventory Management System</b> is "Manual".</li>
 <ol><b>Eg:</b> If suppose the Name of Party is "AP PF", Sales Order # is "SO-1210-0006", Date is "05.01.2011", Transporter is "Own", Bag Code is "BG101", No.Of Bags is "10", Lot# is "10060", Serial# is "10060100601", Mode of Transportation is "By Train", RR# is "4215321451", Time Of Dispatch is "24hrs" and Freight Amount is "100" <br/>
 You have to select <em style="color:#0066FF">AP PF</em> for "Party", <em style="color:#0066FF">SO-1210-0006</em> for "Sales Order #", <em style="color:#0066FF">05.01.2011</em> for "Date", <em style="color:#0066FF">Own</em> for "Transporter", <em style="color:#0066FF">By Train</em> for "Mode Of Transportation" and <em style="color:#0066FF">BG101</em> for "No.Of"(Type Of Bags).<br/>
 You have to enter <em style="color:#0066FF">4215321451</em> for "RR#", <em style="color:#0066FF">10</em> for "No.Of", <em style="color:#0066FF">10060</em> for "Lot#", <em style="color:#0066FF">10060100601</em> FOR "Serial#", <em style="color:#0066FF">24hrs</em> for "Time Of Dispatch" and <em style="color:#0066FF">100</em> for "Freight".</ol>
 <li>Once filled click on 'SAVE' button to save the Pack Slip or 'CANCEL' to exit.</li>
</ol>
</div> <!--end of ordertocash_trans_addpackslip-->
</body>
</html>